PfiIONConnection is a BusinessClass
    owned by pfi
    prefix is PfiIO
	contains environment data
	disable data area copy
		preserve target data
    default label is "IONConnection"
 
    Ontology
        symbolic key is PfiIONConnection

    Patterns
        implements CRUD
        implements LightweightAuditing
        disable AuditIndex
        disable AsOfDateProcessing
        disable EffectiveDated
        implements DynamicCreation

    Persistent Fields

        JDBCDriver  is Alpha size up to 256
        DatabaseURL is Alpha size up to 256
        User        is Alpha size 100
        Password    is Password
        DbSchema    is Alpha size up to 50
        EnablePulse is Boolean
        LogicalId   is Alpha size up to 250
        	
	Field Rules
		JDBCDriver
			required
		DatabaseURL
			required
		        
	Derived Fields
        CanShowFields is a NativeField
        	type is Boolean
            default label is "FieldsShown"
    
        JDBCDriverDisplay is a DerivedField
            type is Alpha size 256
            default label is "JDBCDriver"
            if (CanShowFields)
                return JDBCDriver
            else
                return "JDBC Driver"  
        
        DatabaseURLDisplay is a DerivedField
            type is Alpha size 256
            default label is "DatabaseURL"
            if (CanShowFields)
                return DatabaseURL
            else
                return "Database URL"  
        
    
    Actions
        Create is a Create Action
        Update is an Update Action
        Delete is a Delete Action             
        
        TestConnection is an Instance Action
